title: NYX Eyebrow Cake Powder, Black/Gray
description: Our recipe for cooking up exquisite eyebrows includes wax, tools and a pair of complementary powders, black and gray, which can be customized to create the ideal shade. Each eyebrow cake powder kit includes a slanted brush and a round wand to shape, style and tame eyebrows.

title: NYX Single Eye Shadow, Dark Brown, 2.5 g
description: Richly pigmented eye shadows in over 162 shades. Soft and silky NYX cosmetics single eye shadows are great on their own or blended for a beautiful prism of colors. This top-selling eye shadow is formulated for long-lasting wear.

title: NYX Cream Blush, Tea Rose, 0.12-Ounce
description: Rouge cream blush offers radiant, long-lasting color in the form of a velvety smooth cream. The creamy texture provides a dewy glow for natural, fresh color.

title: Essie Ridge Filler Base Coat, 0.46 oz
description: The ultimate nail foundation for nails with ridges. Gives natural nails with ridges or discoloration a smooth, even base. Its ingredients leave a translucent finish, the perfect base for manicures
